        "subject": "LU-3398 libcfs: Fix NULL pointer dereference in dump_trace()",
        "message": "LU-3398 libcfs: Fix NULL pointer dereference in dump_trace()\n\nThe walk_stack field of struct stacktrace_ops is used\nin dump_trace(), but it is not inited by Lustre-1.8.X.\nThe problem is already fixed in Lustre-2.1 in LU-73, but\nthe patch is not landed in Lustre-1.8.X.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <pkuelelixi@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I0d7fac2256c6f95ad79262e6fe9e0e8cac6b1a0f\n"
      },
